    <item>
      <title>赞比亚与债券持有人达成协议，这是长达数年传奇的关键胜利</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/zambia-agrees-deal-with-bondholders-key-win-in-years-long-saga</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚已同意重组 30 亿美元的欧元债券，扫清了阻碍其为期三年的避免债务违约努力的关键障碍，并对其他寻求债权人交易的国家产生影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/zambia-agrees-deal-with-bondholders-key-win-in-years-long-saga</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:24:02 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚德尼称标普明年可能触及 6,000 点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-25/yardeni-says-s-p-could-hit-6-000-next-year-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Yardeni Research 总裁 Ed Yardeni 表示，明年标普 500 指数可能会达到 6,000 点，而我们现在正处于牛市。他还表示，美联储仍坚持2%的通胀目标。他在“彭博监视”节目中。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-25/yardeni-says-s-p-could-hit-6-000-next-year-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:14:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国总理表示国家2024年目标开局良好</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/china-s-premier-says-nation-off-to-good-start-on-2024-goals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[李强总理表示，自 2024 年初以来，中国经济复苏一直在改善，并强调政府在接待众多知名人士时努力展现信心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/china-s-premier-says-nation-off-to-good-start-on-2024-goals</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:13:29 GMT</pubDate>
