    <item>
      <title>最新出售后，英国不再拥有国民西敏寺银行的控股权</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/uk-no-longer-has-controlling-stake-in-natwest-after-latest-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府不再被视为 NatWest Group Plc 的控股股东，因为它继续加快退出在金融危机中救助的银行。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/uk-no-longer-has-controlling-stake-in-natwest-after-latest-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 13:05:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>穆迪认为债务谈判将释放赞比亚债券增长潜力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/zambia-bonds-gain-as-moody-s-sees-debt-talks-unlocking-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[赞比亚的美元债券走强，因为该国正在努力完成拖延已久的债务重组，穆迪投资者服务公司表示，该协议将成为更广泛经济改革的催化剂。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/zambia-bonds-gain-as-moody-s-sees-debt-talks-unlocking-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 12:39:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>联合利华首席执行官暗示荷兰在冰淇淋上市斗争中处于领先地位</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/unilever-ceo-hints-dutch-could-win-fight-for-ice-cream-listing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[联合利华公司首席执行官表示，阿姆斯特丹可能会击败伦敦，以 170 亿欧元（合 184 亿美元）的价格在联合利华旗下冰淇淋部门上市。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/unilever-ceo-hints-dutch-could-win-fight-for-ice-cream-listing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 11:21:14 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于投资者权衡反对派的选举势头，塞内加尔债券下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-bonds-sink-as-investors-weigh-opposition-s-electoral-momentum</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞内加尔的主权美元债券扭转了跌势，从当天新兴市场中表现最差的债券转为表现最好的债券，因为投资者押注这个西非国家将获得稳定的政府，而巴西鲁·迪奥马耶·法耶(Bassirou Diomaye Faye)则缓和了他在2017年期间概述的一些极端政策措施。竞选活动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-25/senegal-s-bonds-sink-as-investors-weigh-opposition-s-electoral-momentum</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 25 Mar 2024 09:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
